      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't believe how gorgeous this ride is\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition. No scratches, no dents, and that interior still feels brand new! It drives like a dream and is ready for a new home where it'll be just as loved. Come take a look, you're going to fall in love!",
