    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a recently overhauled double-VANOS system, ensuring structural and mechanical longevity. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. The chassis remains taut with factory-spec bushings, and the paint depth is consistent across all panels. A true turn-key investment for the discerning driver seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
