    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo is a superlative example of A80 engineering, preserved in showroom condition. At its heart is the legendary 2JZ-GTE 3.0L inline-six, featuring its original sequential turbocharging system for seamless boost response. Power is routed through the coveted Getrag V160 six-speed manual gearbox to a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis retains its structural integrity with all original VIN tags intact, complemented by a perfectly tuned double-wishbone suspension. Recent diagnostic logs confirm factory-spec compression across all cylinders and zero parasitic draw. This is a mechanically pristine, turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
